pidemia, acne, and venous thrombosis.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/179879/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, More', 'Megestrol acetate, Ulipristal, Estetrol, Megestrol acetate, Progesterone, Megestrol acetate, Progesterone', 1767369485);
